{"id":546,"parent_id":0,"book_id":8,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":546,"title":"Gilgal","subtitle":"","short_title":"Gilgal","uri":"/scriptures/bd/gilgal","content":[["div",{"id":"t1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/gilgal.t1","order":".000.1423"},[".title","Gilgal"],["div",{"id":"p1","uri":"/scriptures/bd/gilgal.p1","order":".000.1424"},["i","A wheel or circle of stones."],"(1) The place near Jericho at which the Israelite camp was made on the first night after crossing the Jordan (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/4.19"},"Josh. 4:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/5.10"},"5:10"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/10"},"10"],"). Here the 12 stones from the Jordan were set up as a monument to the parting of the Jordan River by the power of God. It was a sacred city in the time of Saul (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/10.8"},"1 Sam. 10:8"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/11.14-15"},"11:14–15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/13.4,15"},"13:4, 15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/15.12-33"},"15:12–33"],"); but later it was the scene of idolatrous worship (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/4.15"},"Hosea 4:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.15"},"9:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/12.11"},"12:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/4.4"},"Amos 4:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/5.5"},"5:5"],")."],["div",{"id":"p2","uri":"/scriptures/bd/gilgal.p2","order":".000.1425"},"(2) A place near Bethel, visited by Elijah and Elisha (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.30"},"Deut. 11:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.1"},"2 Kgs. 2:1"],")."],["div",{"id":"p3","uri":"/scriptures/bd/gilgal.p3","order":".000.1426"},"(3)",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/12.23"},"Josh. 12:23"],"."]]],"refs":null}
